{"timestamp":1774427217259,"source_app":"agentic-harness","session_id":"509bd9b9-5dfa-4634-8c82-984aeab86ca6","hook_event_type":"PreToolUse","tool_name":"Write","tool_use_id":"toolu_017TccitRvQTb3JqnqeoySn3","payload":{"session_id":"509bd9b9-5dfa-4634-8c82-984aeab86ca6","transcript_path":"/Users/auto/.claude/projects/-Users-auto-agentic-harness-apps-mas-trees-bdf67753/509bd9b9-5dfa-4634-8c82-984aeab86ca6.jsonl","cwd":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/bdf67753","permission_mode":"bypassPermissions","hook_event_name":"PreToolUse","tool_name":"Write","tool_input":{"file_path":"/Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/bdf67753/specs/patch/patch-add-unit-tests-free-trial-cta-filtering.md","content":"# Patch: Add unit tests for free-trial CTA filtering in processCTAs\n\n## Metadata\nadw_id: ``\nreview_change_request: `Issue #1: No unit tests added for the new free-trial CTA filtering logic. The existing processCTAs test block in web-components/test/hydrate.test.js has no cases covering: (1) trial CTAs filtered on plans variants, (2) non-trial CTAs preserved on plans variants, (3) non-plans variants unaffected, or (4) empty-CTA-array edge case after filtering. Resolution: Add test cases to the processCTAs describe block in web-components/test/hydrate.test.js covering the four scenarios above. Severity: tech_debt`\n\n## Issue Summary\n**Original Spec:** specs/issue-bdf67753-adw-1d78f7d6-sdlc_planner-hide-free-trial-ctas-plan-pages.md\n**Issue:** The `processCTAs` function in `hydrate.js` was updated to filter free-trial CTAs (those whose `data-analytics-id` matches entries in `FREE_TRIAL_CTA_IDS`) when the variant is one of `PLANS_VARIANTS`. However, no unit tests were added for this new behavior.\n**Solution:** Add four `it()` test cases to the `processCTAs` describe block in `web-components/test/hydrate.test.js` covering the four scenarios described in the review change request.\n\n## Files to Modify\n\n- `web-components/test/hydrate.test.js` \u2014 add four test cases to the existing `processCTAs` describe block (after line 284, before the closing `}`).\n\n## Implementation Steps\n\n### Step 1: Add test \u2014 trial CTAs filtered on a plans variant\nInside the `processCTAs` describe block, add a test that passes a `ctas` field containing a checkout link with `data-analytics-id=\"free-trial\"` and calls `processCTAs` with variant `'plans'`. Assert that the footer element contains zero buttons (the trial CTA was removed).\n\n- CTA HTML: `<a is=\"checkout-link\" data-wcs-osi=\"abm\" data-analytics-id=\"free-trial\" class=\"accent\">Free Trial</a>`\n- Call: `processCTAs(fields, merchCard, aemFragmentMapping, 'plans')`\n- Assert: `footer.children` has length `0`\n\n### Step 2: Add test \u2014 non-trial CTAs preserved on plans variant\nAdd a test with a mix of one trial CTA (`data-analytics-id=\"free-trial\"`) and one non-trial CTA (`data-analytics-id=\"buy-now\"`) calling `processCTAs` with variant `'plans'`. Assert only the non-trial button remains.\n\n- CTA HTML: two `<a>` tags, one with `data-analytics-id=\"free-trial\"`, one with `data-analytics-id=\"buy-now\"`\n- Call: `processCTAs(fields, merchCard, aemFragmentMapping, 'plans')`\n- Assert: `footer.children` has length `1`; the remaining button text is `'Buy Now'`\n\n### Step 3: Add test \u2014 non-plans variant is unaffected\nAdd a test with the same trial CTA calling `processCTAs` with a non-plans variant (e.g., `'ccd-slice'`). Assert the trial CTA is **not** removed.\n\n- CTA HTML: `<a is=\"checkout-link\" data-wcs-osi=\"abm\" data-analytics-id=\"free-trial\" class=\"accent\">Free Trial</a>`\n- Call: `processCTAs(fields, merchCard, aemFragmentMapping, 'ccd-slice')`\n- Assert: `footer.children` has length `1`\n\n### Step 4: Add test \u2014 all CTAs filtered results in empty footer\nAdd a test where all provided CTAs are trial CTAs, calling `processCTAs` with variant `'plans-v2'`. Assert the footer element exists but is empty.\n\n- CTA HTML: two trial links \u2014 `data-analytics-id=\"free-trial\"` and `data-analytics-id=\"seven-day-trial\"`\n- Call: `processCTAs(fields, merchCard, aemFragmentMapping, 'plans-v2')`\n- Assert: `footer` exists and `footer.children` has length `0`\n\n## Validation\n\n```bash\n# From the web-components directory\ncd /Users/auto/agentic-harness/apps/mas/trees/bdf67753/web-components\nnpm test -- --grep \"processCTAs\"\n```\n\nOr run the full hydrate test file:\n\n```bash\nnpx wtr test/hydrate.test.js --node-resolve\n```\n\nAll four new test cases should pass with zero regressions on existing `processCTAs` tests.\n\n## Patch Scope\n**Lines of code to change:** ~60\u201380 lines added (four `it()` blocks)\n**Risk level:** low\n**Testing required:** Run the `processCTAs` describe block; verify all existing tests still pass and all four new tests pass.\n"},"tool_use_id":"toolu_017TccitRvQTb3JqnqeoySn3"}}
